 src/OpenClaw.Shared/SettingsData.cs           |  19 ++-
 src/OpenClaw.Shared/VoiceModeSchema.cs        |  94 ++++++++++--
 src/OpenClaw.Tray.WinUI/App.xaml.cs           |   2 +-
 .../Controls/VoiceSettingsPanel.xaml          |   4 +-
