From 82e295879529b44abffb84a1f93e437dbbe388a8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nich Overend <nich@nixnet.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Mar 2026 00:32:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 32/83] Add voice control and configuration APIs

---
